name: Mission and Well-Being Impact
description: Mission and Well-Being Impact is a combination of Mission Prevalence and Public Well-Being Impact.

values.name: Low
values.description: Mission Prevalence:Minimal AND Public Well-Being Impact:Minimal

values.name: Medium
values.description: Mission Prevalence:Support AND Public Well-Being Impact:(Minimal OR Material)

values.name: High
values.description: Mission Prevalence:Essential OR Public Well-Being Impact:(Irreversible)
